    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my favorite car! It\u2019s been a total rockstar for me and is still in wonderful shape for its next adventure. It shows a little bit of character from the road, but it\u2019s been well-cared for and is ready to hit the pavement today. Super fun to drive and very reliable\u2014come check it out and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32500.0,
