    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This engine retains its signature linear power delivery with individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced dual-VANOS system utilizing upgraded seals for optimal camshaft timing. The chassis has been addressed at the critical points, including professional rear subframe reinforcement and the installation of poly-bushes to eliminate deflection. Power is sent through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, both of which operate without noise or hesitation. The suspension has been upgraded to Bilstein monotube dampers, providing superior rebound and compression characteristics over stock. While the paint exhibits minor road rash consistent with enthusiast use, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance are top-tier. Recent fluid analysis confirms the rod bearings are within spec, making this an ideal candidate for a technical owner who prioritizes driving dynamics.",
